ote-sensing.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/imps/publications/screw-shell/index.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mpa/publications/solitary-user-guide.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/species/sharks/sawfish/publications/sawfishes-age.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mbp/publications/north/losc-carpentaria.html	http://austmus.gov.au/invertebrates/pdf/marineoverview.pdf	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/imps/publications/workshop-seastar.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mbp/publications/north/north-brochure.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/publications/freshwater-sawfish-pristis-microdon.html	http://environment.gov.au/marinereserves/publications/north-west-social-economic-assessment.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mpa/publications/cod-grounds-swath-survey.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/imps/publications/antifouling-framework.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mbp/publications/south-east/se-bioregionalisation.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/pollution/dumping/publications/artificial-reef-factsheet.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/publications/grey-nurse-biology.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mbp/publications/general/goals-nrsmpa.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mpa/publications/conservation-assessment-bonney.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mpa/publications/ashmore-corals.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mbp/publications/north-west/nw-socio-economic-overview.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mbp/publications/east/sedimentology-geomorphology.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mpa/publications/cartier-plan.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mpa/publications/gab-values.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/publications/olive-ridley-nt.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/publications/identification-guide/index.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mbp/publications/north/tradition-legislation.html	http://environment.gov.au/coasts/mbp/publications/south-west/sw-flinders-pelagic-fishes.ht oop	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flottillenadmiral	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Deptford_(U53)&action=edit&redlink=1	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/German_submarine_U-126_(1940)	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/German_submarine_U-3524	http://uboat.net/men/endrass.htm	http://uboat.net/men/lassen.htm	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=List_of_successful_U-boat_commanders&oldid=663765972	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:UserLogin&returnto=List+of+successful+U-boat+commanders&type=signup	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Otto_Steinbrinck	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Engelbert_Endrass	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SS_Athenia	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/German_submarine_U-22_(1936)	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=List_of_successful_U-boat_commanders&action=edit	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walther_Schwieger	http://uboat.net/men/rosenstiel.htm	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karl-Heinz_Moehle	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lawyer	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/P._O._Box_1142	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bordeaux	http://uboat.net/men/emmermann.htm	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:All_articles_with_unsourced_statements	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georg_Schewe	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johann_Mohr	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Laertes_(T137)&action=edit&redlink=1	http://uboat.net/men/schnee.htm	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reinhold_Saltzwedel	http://uboat.net/men/gysae.htm	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Herbert_Schultze.jpg	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herbert_Kuppisch	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Soviet_occupation_zone	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Max_Valentiner.jpg	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/German_submarine_U-147_(1940)	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Torpedo	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bay_of_Biscay	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Konteradmiral	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Battle_of_the_River_Plate	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed	https://en.wikipedia.org/wi ex.php?title=Portal:Battleships/WikiProjects&action=edit	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SMS_Prinz_Eugen	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russian_battleship_Petropavlovsk_(1911)	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Braunschweig-class_battleship	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Massachusetts_(BB-2)	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_battlecruisers_of_the_Royal_Navy	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russian_battleship_Rostislav	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SMS_Zr%C3%ADnyi	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMS_Glorious	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMS_Repulse_(1916)	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russian_battleship_Tri_Sviatitelia	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Dolphin_(PG-24)	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/German_cruiser_Prinz_Eugen	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMS_Lion_(1910)

anean_Sea	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Book&bookcmd=book_creator&referer=German+submarine+U-303	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:WhatLinksHere/German_submarine_U-303	http://uboat.net/boats/patrols/u303.html	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toulon	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=German_submarine_U-303&action=info	http://uboat.net/allies/merchants/ships/2678.html	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Year%27s_Day	http://uboat.net/boats/u303.htm	http://u-boot-archiv.de/dieboote/u0303.html	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=German_submarine_U-303&printable=yes

ower-class_corvette	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hydrophone	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMS_Stoic	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Percy_Lockhart_Harnam_Noble	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Air_Historical_Branch	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Medal	http://uboatarchive.net/POWInternmentMail.htm	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&printable=yes	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RAF_Museum	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Naval_ships_of_Germany_captured_by_the_United_Kingdom_during_World_War_II	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Submarines_of_the_Royal_Navy	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hugh_Sebag-Montefiore	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chlorine	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Test_depth	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oxy-fuel_welding_and_cutting	http://uboatarchive.net/U-570BritishReport.htm	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Random	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Book&bookcmd=render_article&arttitle=HMS+Graph&oldid=667446216&writer=rdf2latex	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shaped_charge	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deck_gun	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=8	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=9	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=6	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Distinguished_Flying_Cross_(United_Kingdom)	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=7	https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-394-58839-8	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=1	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=4	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=5	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=2	https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=HMS_Graph&action=edit&section=3	http://nationalarchives.gov.uk/catalogue/externalrequest.asp?requestreference=ADM253/436	https://en.w
